    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA358-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">1. itu paṭṭapiṉṟai varaiyātu poruḷvayiṟ pirinta kālattut tōḻi yivaḷāṟṟā ḷāyiṉāḷ “iḻantēṉ” eṉak kavaṉṟa vaṟpuṟuttatu.
            2. akkālat tāṟṟāḷāy niṉṟa talaimakaḷ tōḻikkuc colliyatūumām.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">1. This is how the confidante encouraged in a time when [HE] had separated for the sake of wealth without marrying after it had happened, anxious when she who had become unable to bear it said “I have lost [my beauty]”.
            2. It is also what SHE who stood [there], unable to bear it at that time, said to the confidante.</p>
        </div>
      <div xml:id="NA358">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>           peruntō ṇekiḻa vavvari vāṭac</l>
<l>           ciṟumel lākam perumpacap pūra</l>
<l>           viṉṉē māka veṟkaṇṭu nāṇi</l>
<l>           niṉṉoṭu teḷittaṉa rāyiṉu meṉṉatūu</l>
<l>           maṇaṅka lōmpumati vāḻiya nīyeṉak</l>
<l>           kaṇaṅkeḻu kaṭavuṭ kuyarpali tūuyp</l>
<l>           paraviṉam varukañ ceṉmō tōḻi</l>
<l>           peruñcē yiṟaviṉ ṟuyttalai muṭaṅkal</l>
<l>           ciṟuveṇ kākkai nāḷirai peṟūum</l>
<l>           pacumpūṇ vaḻuti maruṅkai yaṉṉaveṉ</l>
<l>           ṉarumpeṟa lāykaviṉ tolaiyap</l>
<l>           pirintāṇ ṭuṟaital valli yōrē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>           Up, friend, let us do reverence, strewing</l>
<l>           high offerings to the gods in a group, [and] come [back],</l>
<l rend="indent4">               saying</l>
<l rend="indent3">               “may you live, beware of tormenting him</l>
<l rend="indent3">                in any way, even if he has sworn on you,</l>
<l rend="indent3">                ashamed at seeing me thus:</l>
<l rend="indent2">               while [my] big shoulders are emaciated, while those lines fade,</l>
<l rend="indent2">               while big pallor creeps up my soft little bosom”,</l>
<l>           – him who is strong [enough] to stay there, separated,</l>
<l rend="indent">               so that my choice beauty difficult to obtain is lost,</l>
<l rend="indent2">               like Maruṅkai of Vaḻuti with green ornaments,</l>
<l rend="indent3">               where the little white crow obtains as daily prey</l>
<l rend="indent4">               something bent with soft head in the big red prawn.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
